  "original_title": "\u0d87\u0db8\u0dd9\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dc0 \u0dc3\u0db8\u0d9c \u0d95\u0db1\u0dd1\u0db8 \u0d9c\u0dd0\u0da7\u0dd4\u0db8\u0d9a\u0da7 \u0dc3\u0dd6\u0daf\u0dcf\u0db1\u0db8\u0dca - \u0d9a\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Ready for any conflict with America - Kim",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The leader of the Democratic People's Republic of Korea, Kim Jong-un, says that his government is ready to fight any mobilization to prevent North Korea's nuclear war power and any US military provocation.",
        "Kim made the announcement while addressing a ceremony to mark the 69th anniversary of the Korean War armistice on July 27.",
        "His latest warnings come as South Korea and the United States move to step up joint military exercises, saying Pyongyang is preparing for an invasion.",
        "This week, the US military conducted live-fire exercises using high-tech Apache helicopters stationed in South Korea for the first time since 2019."
      ],
